svg.title: Final prototype of KidsGive public campaign page.

cc:Work.dc:title: Final prototype of KidsGive public campaign page.
cc:Work.dc:description: Public campaign page is improved in a number of ways: clearer campaign statistics, icons to visualise spending target, collapsible panels to hide secondary information about charity liason, spending and KidsGive's role, message board to connect organiser, donors and charity.

flowRoot.flowPara: Clearer campaign statistics communicate goals and status
Secondary info is easily accessible, but hidden in collapsible panels
Message board connects organiser, donors and charity creating meaning and relationships
Information about charity liason, spending and KidGive's role improves trust and transparency.
